            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Informatiebronnen",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-small\" style=\"color:#000000;\">Deze bronnen kun je gebruiken voor de opdrachten:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-small\" style=\"color:#000000;\">\u2022    <a href=\"http://schoolfotograaf.startbewijs.nl/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Schoolfotograaf</span></a></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "133955"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Afsluiting",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-small\" style=\"color:#000000;\">Heb je de opdrachten af? Vul dan het evaluatieformulier in en lever dit in.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-small\" style=\"color:#000000;\">Het evaluatieformulier vind je op de laatste bladzijde van de opdrachten.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong><br/></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
